column3: “I don't usually rate my strains by their experience due to a bunch of reasons. Anyways this cookie dough is absolute fire. If you see it buy. Buy it in bulk please you will not regret your purchase. As somebody with a HUGE tolerance to most flowers I can say this will knock out even the most seasoned cannabis consumer. Stay Stoney my friends (-; also this is a very saliva leaning strain, thus paranoia suffers beware ...”

“grabbed some cookie dough while a friend was in town and had a great time with it. the first bowl had me eating a pizza and a half. the second bowl had me on the couch watching Bill Nye, the Science Guy, marathon-style.”
“Such a Sensational High. Taste just like girl scout cookies but the high is phenomenal! 10/10 would smoke again”
“If you like to sleep this one's for you”

“What can I say about Cookie Dough? Im high? No, it's needs more. It needs a proper introduction... It's like a fairy grew this strain with her own hands, FUCKING MAGIC! Within ten minutes you begin to fall on a bed of clouds, there is amazing trippy/acid feeling further into the decent from your world to the next. Where do you go from here you ask..? THE KITCHEN to grab yourself a motha loving snack, because the munc...”
“relaxing and talkative. music is a plus”

“Hail Mary Jane, hands down one of the strongest strains I have ever smoked, had me walking like a zombie out of the walking dead! Super sweet almost cheesy berry taste, HEAVY mong and giggles that last almost an hour. Cannot go wrong with this strain, especially if you want to get more mashed than the potatoes on a plate of my mothers chicken dinners!!”
“Nice GSC cut. We have this here in Michigan & wow! Definitely top shelf meds, a little racy at the start with a bit of paranoid, but if you can wait it out, she will take care of you real well”
“I dig it 😁 bout to twist one now cookies for breakfast , cookies for lunch, and cookies for supper time with this strain of cookies I can eat cookies anytime”

“Beautiful blissful high. Sweet sort of skunk flavour. Tingly sensation throughout, helping melt chronic pain and headache away. Appetite for the first time in months. The mind effect's aren't overwhelming, just right to relax. If I had more I'd be passed out in bed right now, but for now I'm chillen. 1/2 a dab in. My husband loves it too, killed all of his pain instantly. This is a true hybrid with the mind/body effe...”

“I'm high as fuck. 

I can't even multi task. 

What do I think of this strain?

 I'm high as the nuts of a fucking giraffe.”
“Pretty decent strain. Effects are pretty long lasting. Can be a little overwhelming at first... so take it slow with this one.”
“WTF is this shit crossed with. I've been smoking for 15 years and shit has me straight gripping my balls tripping everytime.”

“The force is strong in this one. It hits hard, it hits fast and it hits you everywhere. Even for a veteran like me this strain is overwhelming. Great for getting away from it, but forget any and all notions of productivity.”

“So far my favorite of the Cookies ranking equal to the Blueberry Cookies mainly for their taste.  The latter was just super sweet with an edge of skunk, but this Cookie Dough was not so.  Rather bland with a little bite on the tail end which is immediately felt.  With each hit the sensation becomes stronger seeming endless.  Meaning the sky is the limit so if you want to get ripped keep going.

Really keep puffing aw...”
“Feeeeee - nominal! Fucked me up so bad I was waiting at wrong bus stops and walking in wrong directions. A most pleasurable brain melt!”
“Pretty decent strain. Effects are pretty long lasting. Can be a little overwhelming at first... so take it slow with this one.”
“Cookie dough is a very relaxing strain when it comes to relieving stress. I believe that the cookie flavor comes with the after taste and always leaves an uplifting vibe.”
“the description is rite on for me.”
“Awesome strain, dense  buds. Not really frosty but it's super stony!”
“My favorite strain!! Really helps my anxiety and body pain. Makes great dense fragrant buds”

“as i sit here breathing after smoking, i taste the raw cookie dough. i had read the info and reviews before i bought it. i decided one hit at a time, which quickly became two. i have been repeating the cycle for hours. i feel the sedating effect whilst completely lucid and down for anything. i appreciate the high THC level so as i'm not smoking so much as to cough. this is fire for those familiar with flower. i bough...”
“Makes a fellow mellow. Smooth burn. Body high is relaxing. Nice smoke.”

“I had to replace an OG cartridge that either got too much light or too cold and crystallized (b/c the live-resin); Anyway I traded in cookies and dream in for this and I am seriously glad I did, I get cluster headaches and this hasn’t been slowing them like cbd but boy it’s brought a 9 down to a 6-7. (—on a 1-10 pain scale, like suicidal pain). But CBD nearly kills em like shrooms. Anyways, I have anxiety and mild Sa...”
“My rapper friend got some of this in, not sure if its because weed is literally more common than pennies in his pocket and he packed the joint as a fattie, but i was slumped”
“Good taste just like real cookie dough.”
“very good, very pungent, strong head high”

“Totally different from GSC!! Really amazing as a social buffer, definitely a mood-lifter. Had some today before going on a hike, colors were way more colorful- amazingly intense effects. Kind of puts me in a kush hole when it hits but once you get past that it’s incredible.”

“One for the connoisseurs!  This dank, sweet and dry, baked beauty will give the newcomer trouble! A friendly, true to name kick comes with a tickley, moreish inhale and overall  10/10 all round high,  making this strain a great choice to many people  for many reasons.”
“Great Strain Boutta twist one up now for breakfast, another for lunch and more for supper time with this particular strain of cookies I can consume cookies anytime 😁”
“very nice mellow”
“Bought some wax of this strain and its an excellent balance. Relaxing and talkative. music is definitely a plus.”
“Got half oZ of this amazing bud as i was told great things about it, Nice sweet taste and a smooth smoke it worked wonders for my deppression, would definitely reccomend to anyone”
“Very good daytime high. I could talk about ten things right now." says J”"
“Nice for a wake and bake”
“Super relaxing. This stuff was amazing.”
“Tastes like cookie dough... smells like cookie dough. Great day timer as a sativa dominate. Awesome balance for pain & zen! ✌🏿”

“OUTSTANDING!!!
Every review is true! (but that one)
Best stone I've had in some time. 
mo-chao friends”
“The effect that it has is awesome! You have that creating relaxed feeling without the lazy, couch potato body effect.”
“Love this strain!  Nice and heady at first followed by relaxation.  Also, a little goes a long way!”

“Love Thise flavors, sweet/sour pungent forrest berries, love the head High a bit trippy but lovely body relaxing, had me a crazy munches. For everybody who likes indica strains, that wanna relaxing bodyhigh whit a calming effekt on your mind also, Not for beginners.”
“Amazing Strain! Covered in Orange pistil and frosty trichomes! Great aroma, even better than GSC! Effects are awesome! Hits really hard, really quickly! Another killer GSC pheno!”
“@krd_inc made some tasteeee budder with this .. smells and taste yummy ..... litte pitter pat in my chest but not noided!!!”
“Good”
“Dirt. Weak dirt. Never again”
